{"TopicId":137217,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Expand \u0022hack gravity\u0022","CreatedByName":"TinfoilChef","CreatedById":43840,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T01:30:17Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TinfoilChef","CreatedById":43840,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T01:30:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe \u0022hack gravity\u0022 item on the ALT\u002BF12 menu is often very handy for testing designs but it\u0027s usefulness could be expanded by including options to set the gravity to what you would encounter on other bodies.\u00A0 This would be especially useful for designs intended for Eve and Tylo\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Knaapie","CreatedById":156655,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T02:18:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n^^ So you got a gravity hack, infinite fuel and you want\u00A0to hack more?? ^^ \u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:0.0:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_shocked.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:0.0:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere are ways to edit save files and bring ships into orbit anywhere, there is a mod for this as well (forgot the name) \u00A0Can someone provide some links? \u00A0(edit: hyper edit !)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThese features are easy accessible for alpha and beta players. And would more likely be removed than extended... \u00A0sooo.. \u00A0 be quiet \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/34785-105-hyperedit-v142-nov-11-2015-teleporter-orbit-planet-editor-more/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-04-18T02:19:38Z\u0022 title=\u002204/18/2016 02:19  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EApril 18, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Knaapie\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T02:55:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156655-knaapie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156655\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156655-knaapie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Knaapie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Firstly not all of us are coders. Secondly hyperedit is kraken bait like no other thing around. Having tunable hack gravity stock at some point would be nice.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Blaarkies","CreatedById":153700,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T04:59:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222519666\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137217\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460948157\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002278020\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022AlamoVampire\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, AlamoVampire said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156655-knaapie/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u0022156655\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/156655-knaapie/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Knaapie\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0Firstly not all of us are coders. Secondly hyperedit is kraken bait like no other thing around. Having tunable hack gravity stock at some point would be nice.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats a way better idea. We should not need to open up the cheats menu to test ships...we should be able to just test them, need some way to implement\u00A0tunable gravity in some \u0022simulation\u0022 thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Knaapie","CreatedById":156655,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-04-18T13:04:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222519777\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022137217\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221460955591\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022153700\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Blaarkies\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Blaarkies said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThats a way better idea. We should not need to open up the cheats menu to test ships...we should be able to just test them, need some way to implement\u00A0tunable gravity in some \u0022simulation\u0022 thing?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe simulator within the simulator.. That\u0027s kinda funny.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn a\u00A0game, where Kerbals use tail fins lying on the side of the road, slap them on a rocket and go to space with them... \u00A0I\u0027d say the Squad wants you to fail, crash and burn on different bodies\u00A0in space.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-i